Package: LibeRation
Title: Nonlinear Mixed-Effects Modelling
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sven C.", "van Dijkman", email = "svdijkman@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: NONMEM-style population PK/PD estimation with FO, FOCE, FOCEI,
    SAEM, Laplace, IMP, and full Bayesian MCMC. Supports configurable
    residual and omega structures, covariates, GOF tables, bootstrap SE,
    NONMEM control import, and project workflows. Uses LibeRtAD for AD.
